Text: FW Line Liquid Sample SummaryTWxlsOriginal Message From McCurdy Richard Sent Thursday October AM To nroncom Cc Anderson David Blevins C Boschee Rodney Burke Carol Lytle Dan Riddle Glen Wong Melvin Subject Line Liquid Sample SummaryTWxls Line Liquid Sample SummaryTWxls Hi Larry Attached please find the latest Line pipeline liquid sample test summary for the Hinkley and Kettleman districts Results include those taken through the first week in October Ive also included test results from ongoing Mojave filter separator liquid sampling Let me know if you have any questions See you at our upcoming meeting in Las Vegas on Thanks Rich Rich McCurdy PGE California Gas Transmission Gas System Maintenance Technical Support Co Phone Outside No Pager Fax Line Liquid Sample SummaryTWxls
